cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a dataset for 3D perception tasks using event-based cameras. The use of inertial measurement units (IMU), motion capture, and GPS also suggests that it may belong to the robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The development of algorithms for event-based cameras may also fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
